{"article_id":"NZOlV9aWumyIOuf7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Chief Justice John Roberts joined the Supreme Court 's liberal wing on Thursday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"in temporarily blocking a Louisiana law","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that would have placed restrictions on abortion clinics ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"in the high court 's first major ruling on abortion since the confirmation of Associate Justice Brett Kavanaugh .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The ruling comes","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"as Roberts ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"who was appointed by President George W. Bush ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"has increasingly and deliberately sought to present the federal judiciary as nonpartisan , amid a flurry of attacks from progressive groups","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"arguing","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that the Supreme Court 's new conservative majority imperils the country .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Last year , in a highly unusual statement , Roberts rebuked President Trump","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"for criticizing partisanship in the federal judiciary .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"The Louisiana law is virtually identical to a Texas measure","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"the justices struck down three years ago by a 5-3 vote , shortly after the death of Justice Antonin Scalia .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Roberts dissented in that case ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"when he was not the deciding vote ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and sided with the conservative minority","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that wanted to uphold the anti-abortion law","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"-- making his decision on Thursday a significant reversal .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"The justices decided in a 5-4 vote on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"with Roberts as the swing vote ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that they will not allow Louisiana to put into effect a law","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that requires abortion providers to have admitting privileges at nearby hospitals .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The Supreme Court is set to issue a final ruling on the merits of the case later ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"and Thursday 's majority ruling did not spell out a rationale .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"In the 2016 Texas case , the Supreme Court held","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that the admitting-privileges requirement \" provides few , if any , health benefits for women ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"poses a substantial obstacle to women","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"seeking abortions ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"and constitutes an ' undue burden ' on their constitutional right","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to do so . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The court 's four more conservative justices ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"including Neil Gorsuch and Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"would have allowed the Louisiana law to take effect .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Kavanaugh wrote a dissent","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"explaining his vote ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"while he respects the 2016 precedent ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"the court 's action was premature","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"because the state had made clear","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"it would allow abortion providers an additional 45 days","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"to obtain admitting privileges","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"before it started enforcing the law .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"If the doctors succeed ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"they can continue performing abortions ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"but","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"if they fail ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"they could return to court ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Kavanaugh wrote .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"The other conservative justices ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"although they dissented ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"did not join Kavanaugh 's opinion .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"`` The parties have offered , in essence , competing predictions \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"about what would happen","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"if the law were implemented ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Kavanaugh said in his dissent .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" If we denied the stay","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"[ and allowed the law to be implemented ] ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"that question could be readily and quickly answered","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"without disturbing the status quo","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"or causing harm to the parties or the affected women ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and without this court ' s further involvement . \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"ANALYSIS :","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"ROBERTS ' REBUKE OF TRUMP WAS HIGHLY POLITICAL AND INAPPROPRIATE","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"The law was set to take effect Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"but last Friday , Justice Samuel Alito temporarily halted its implementation","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"so that the justices could review arguments .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Observers said","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that at least one and maybe two of Louisiana 's three abortion clinics would have to close","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"if the law were allowed to take effect .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"A federal appeals court","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that upheld the law , however ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"it 's not clear that any clinic would close .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"The chief justice 's overt attempts","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"to project ideological balance on the Supreme Court","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"have heightened","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"since the contentious confirmation of Kavanaugh ostensibly gave conservatives a 5-4 majority on the Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"Many pro-choice groups claimed","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"that Kavanaugh 's confirmation amounted to a cataclysmic event ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"with the far-left progressive political action committee Democracy for America warning of the imminent `` deaths of countless women . ''","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"TRUMP :","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"NINTH CIRCUIT WOULD OVERTURN MY TURKEY PARDON","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"IF IT COULD","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Last November , Roberts openly disputed President Trump 's comments","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"that the nation has `` Obama judges '' and partisan hacks on the courts .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"The move marked a highly unusual challenge to the White House from a sitting Supreme Court justice ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"and prompted some observers to accuse Roberts of naivete .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"\" What we have is an extraordinary group of dedicated judges","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"doing their level best","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"to do equal right to those","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"appearing before them , \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Roberts said in the head-turning statement .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"But Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"who has long attacked the liberal Ninth Circuit Court of Appeals as biased and a `` total disaster , ''","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"fired back immediately .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"\" Sorry Chief Justice John Roberts ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"but you do indeed have ' Obama judges , '","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and they have a much different point of view than the people","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"who are charged with the safety of our country , \"","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"\" It would be great","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"if the 9th Circuit was indeed an ' independent judiciary , '","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"but if it is","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"why are so many opposing view","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"( on Border and Safety )","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"cases filed there ,","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"and why are a vast number of those cases overturned , \"","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Trump continued .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"\" Please study the numbers ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"they are shocking .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"We need protection and security","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"- these rulings are making our country unsafe !","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Very dangerous and unwise ! \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"The debate over the Louisiana bill comes amid a renewed national debate on abortion law .","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"Senate Democrats on Monday blocked a GOP effort","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"to introduce a billl","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"meant to protect abortion survivors ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"which came in response to comments last week by Virginia Democratic Gov . Ralph Northam","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"that seemingly endorsed post-birth abortions in certain cases .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Nebraska Republican Sen. Ben Sasse sought unanimous consent","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"to pass the Born-Alive Abortion Survivors Protection Act ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"which would have required","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"that `` any health care practitioner present '' at the time of a birth `` exercise the same degree of professional skill , care , and diligence","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"to preserve the life and health of the child","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"as a reasonably diligent and conscientious health care practitioner would render to any other child born alive at the same gestational age . ''","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"The bill ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"which exempted the mother","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"involved in the birth from prosecution ,","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"also would have required practitioners to `` ensure that the child","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"born alive","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"is immediately transported and admitted to a hospital . ''","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"It prescribed a possible term of imprisonment of up to five years for violations ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"not including penalties for first-degree murder","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that could also apply .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Democrats dismissed the bill as little more than a political stunt .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":199,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":148,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":140,"right":147,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":0,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":138,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":4,"right":144,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":141,"right":143,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":7,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":160,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":154,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":149,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":18,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":150,"right":151,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"c